# hops
# oil descriptions from http://beerlegends.com

Humulene oil, essential oil # woody, herbal fragrance, woody, spicy flavor
Myrcene oil, essential oil #grapes, peaches, vanilla, wine, balsamic, woody, green, herbaceous, and peppery fragrance, citrusy, earthy to metallic flavor
Caryophyllene oil, essential oil # woody, peppery, spicy, earthy flavor; woody spicy earthy clove fragrance
Farnesene oil, essential oil #herbal, woody flavor; magnolia flower, citrusy, green, woody vegetative fragrance
Linalool oil, essential oil #sweet, flowery, spicy, woody, lavenderlike fragrance; hop flavor; 20 ppb required to get hop flavor (http://www.mbaa.com/brewresources/Documents/Linalool.pdf)
Geraniol oil, essential oil # floral / estery
b-Pinene oil, essential oil #piney to citrusy

